@model IEnumerable<CRUD5.Models.temployee>
<br />
<br />       <!-- 提交(方法,控制器名稱,提交方式) -->
@using (Html.BeginForm("employeesearch", "Home", FormMethod.Get))
{
    @Html.TextBox("searching") <!-- TextBox裡的tag -->
    <input type="submit" value="搜尋" />
}
<br />
<p>@Html.ActionLink("新增資料", "employeecreate")</p>
<table class="table table-striped">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>廠商編號</th>  <!-- 標題 -->
            <th>廠商名稱</th>
            <th>廠商電話</th>
            <th>廠商地址</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        @if (Model.Count() == 0)
        {
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3" style="color:red">
                    查無資料
                </td>
            </tr>
        }
        else
        {
            foreach (var item in Model)
            {   
                <tr>
                    <td>@item.EId</td>  <!-- 依序放置 -->
                    <td>@item.EName</td>
                    <td>@item.EPhone</td>
                    <td>@item.EAddress</td>
                    <td>
                        @Html.ActionLink("修改", "employeeedit", new { id = item.EId }) |
                        @Html.ActionLink("刪除", "employeedelete", new { id = item.EId })
                    </td>
                </tr>
            }
        }
    </tbody>
</table>

<div>
    @Html.ActionLink("返回", "index")
</div>